column2: Using heroin would not sharpen my concentration.
I could control things better right now if I could use heroin.
If I tried a little heroin right now, I would not be able to stop using more of it.
I want heroin so bad I can almost taste it.
I don’t want to use heroin now.
I would be less irritable now if I could use heroin.
All I want to use now is heroin.
Using heroin would not be very satisfying now.
I would not enjoy using heroin now.
I do not need to use heroin now.
I would not be able to control how much heroin I used if I had some here.
I have an urge for heroin.
I think that I could resist using heroin now.
